## What was built

A secure multi-room chat app — **Express + EJS + SQLite**, listening on **port 5076**.

```
server.js                 App wiring, security middleware, error handling
db.js                     SQLite connection + schema (users, rooms, messages)
models.js                 Prepared-statement data layer (parameterised queries)
middleware/security.js    Auth guard + CSRF (synchronizer token)
routes/auth.js            register / login / logout
routes/rooms.js           list/create rooms, post/delete messages
views/*.ejs               Auto-escaped templates
