- **Headers** — CSP, `X-Content-Type-Options`, `X-Frame-Options`, `Referrer-Policy`, `Permissions-Policy`, HSTS over HTTPS.
- **Errors** — debug off, generic custom error pages, no stack-trace leakage.
- **Secrets** — `SECRET_KEY` read from env, never hardcoded.

